import React, { Component } from "react"; import "./Profile.scss"; import profile from "../../../Assets/image/profile.jpg"; import { connect } from "react-redux"; // import { setUserData } from "../../../Actions"; class Profile extends Component { componentDidMount() { this.props.handleOpenProfile(); } render() { return (
); } } const MapStateToProps = (state) => ({ profileData: state.auth.userData, }); export default connect(MapStateToProps)(Profile);
